outputs.output_descr: The intention of the PPG is to prepare a detailed MSP for the introduction of renewable wave energy technologies for the generation of electric power in Small Coastal Communities in Jamaica requires close cooperation with concerned government entities as well as national stakeholders, and coordination with possible private partnership and bilateral and multilateral financing institutions

project_descr: Introduction of Renewable Wave Energy Technologies for the Generation of Electric Power in Small Coastal Communities in Jamaica
project_title: Introducing Renewable Wave Energy in Jamaica
